text: Orły may refer to: * Orły, Masovian Voivodeship, a village in east-central Poland * Orły, Subcarpathian Voivodeship, a village in south-east Poland * Gmina Orły, rural gmina (administrative district) in Subcarpathian Voivodeship, south-east Poland * Orły-Cesin, village in Sochaczew County, Masovian Voivodeship, in east-central Poland * Orły ("Eagles"), the common name of the Polish Film Awards ==See also== * Orłów (disambiguation)
